data.description: This is the house you've been waiting for! Gorgeous upgraded 2 story home in the highly desired northwest neighborhood of Providence. You can enjoy the Promenade Trail just across the street for a leisure walk or workout. Enjoy some fun and relaxing times at the close by small recreational park with a big grassy area and a playground. The big recreational Huckleberry Park is just a 5 minutes drive away! This house has your desired curb appeal with a lovely front porch and a beautiful paved backyard for entertainment and relaxation. The family room in the front of the house gives some extra space to enjoy. The upstairs hallway has extra space for a small sitting area. Tasteful custom paint throughout the house. The kitchen is a dream come true and will make you enjoy spending time in it, preparing meals and entertain family and friends! The house offers an open floorplan yet it feels cozy and very welcoming. See for yourself and be prepared to fall in love! No SID or LID!
